        <figcaption>台湾前总统马英九启程前往中国大陆祭祖，支持的“中华爱国同心会”和反对的“台湾国”团体都到桃园机场表达诉求，被警察隔离在两端。图为“中华爱国同心会”成员。（庄慧良摄）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2023-03/unnamed_6.jpg?VersionId=pX_puSLoLQ51Qg6apfDO1KeIu6MOJYbJ" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
